propel.core.collections.buffers

Class SharedBuffer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.collections.buffers.CircularBuffer<T>
      • propel.core.collections.buffers.SharedBuffer<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, IBuffer<T>, ReifiedIterable<T>, IShared

    public class SharedBuffer<T>
extends CircularBuffer<T>
implements IShared
    A type-aware thread-safe limited size circular buffer. This collection does not allow nulls to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new SharedBuffer<String>(){}; -OR- new SharedBuffer<String>(String.class);
